Uses of Package
edu.kit.scc.dem.wapsrv.model

  • Packages that use edu.kit.scc.dem.wapsrv.model 
    Package Description
    edu.kit.scc.dem.wapsrv.controller
    Contains controllers that implement the the REST endpoints along with utility classes containing constants.
    edu.kit.scc.dem.wapsrv.model
    Contains the common model interfaces and general model constants
    edu.kit.scc.dem.wapsrv.model.formats
    Contains different formatters
    edu.kit.scc.dem.wapsrv.model.rdf
    Contains the Apache RDF implementation of the common model interfaces and some utility classes
    edu.kit.scc.dem.wapsrv.repository
    Contains the the repository interfaces which are used to interact with the database
    edu.kit.scc.dem.wapsrv.repository.jena
    Contains the Apache Jena specific implementations of the repositories and the Jena RDF backend.
    edu.kit.scc.dem.wapsrv.service
    Contains the the service interfaces and implementations which are used as the bridge between the controllers and the repositories.

  • Classes in edu.kit.scc.dem.wapsrv.model used by edu.kit.scc.dem.wapsrv.model 
    Class and Description
    Annotation
    The annotation interface contains all methods special to annotations.
    AnnotationList
    AnnotationList is a simple list of annotations without the additional metadata of pages.
    Container
    The container interface defines all methods special to containers.
    FormattableObject
    Everything that need to have a String serialization for usage in HTTP response bodies has to implement this interface.
    FormattableObject.Type
    The different types of formattable objects that may exist
    Page
    Page objects need to implement this interface.
    WapObject
    The WapObject that is the base interface Annotation and Container extend
